---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 343
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=God the Only Doer
  - 180
By: St Alphonsus Liguori
---
What honor can our works give to God if we do not perform them
according to His good pleasure? The Lord doth not desire sacrifice,
said the prophet to Saul, but obedience to His will.
